redflag.title: RedFlag swimwear
redflag.subtitle: Website Design
redflag.descriptionSectionTwo: REDFLAG quería expandir la presencia de su marca a otras ciudades y países.  La marca necesitaba una plataforma sólida de comercio electrónico que pudiera proporcionar soluciones de cumplimiento para sus mercados nacionales e internacionales.
redflag.descriptionSectionThree: Desarrollamos su E-commerce en Shopify. Con informes en tiempo real para análisis en el sitio.   Automatización de las operaciones de cumplimiento con cotizaciones a pedido de los proveedores de envío. Rastreo fácilmente de las devoluciones y los reembolsos.
redflag.resultDescription: Gracias a este sitio ha logrado posicionarse sutilmente en la mente de sus clientes como una marca de calidad, característica que le ayudó a ganar una ronda de inversión para su expansión en América Latina y Estados Unidos.
redflag.complementDescriptionOne: We are building the digital marketing architecture to promote new advertising actions and have a better understanding of the audience through an analytics and monitoring plan.
redflag.complementDescriptionTwo: We are currently implementing local and international SEO strategies.

captiva.title: Captiva
captiva.subtitle: Website Design
captiva.descriptionSectionTwo: Implementar estrategias de SEO local e internacional.  Construimos la arquitectura de marketing digital para promover nuevas acciones publicitarias y tener un mejor conocimiento de la audiencia a través de un plan de análisis y seguimiento.
captiva.descriptionSectionThree: A través de un profundo entendimiento de la forma en que buscan, impactar a sus clientes y entendiendo los desafíos de posicionarse en el mercado norteamericano, propusimos un diseño sobrio pero llamativo.
captiva.resultDescription: Crecimiento en posicionamiento web así como captación de clientes. El sitio les ayudó a establecer una estrategia de comunicación sólida y crear una base de clientes importante.
captiva.complementDescriptionOne: We are building the digital marketing architecture to promote new advertising actions and have a better understanding of the audience through an analytics and monitoring plan.
captiva.complementDescriptionTwo: We are currently implementing local and international SEO strategies.

hbo.title: hbo
hbo.subtitle: platform Design
hbo.descriptionSectionTwo: HBO asked us for a tool where they can provide information and commercial resources to the different sales teams associated with their commercial allies. The challenge is to create a consultation space at the time of the telephone sale.This platform supports teams from Mexico, the Caribbean and Latin America.
hbo.descriptionSectionThree: We design and develop a customized platform where the commercial teams can consult the information and content of the HBO, HBOMax and Warner Media platforms. We also created an analytics dashboard of all the actions carried out by the advisors within the platform
hbo.resultDescription: The platform helped them to provide clear and unified information to the different countries and actively assist in the commercial closing.
hbo.complementDescriptionOne: HBO centrally communicates the necessary resources for commercial actions supported by gamification, a chatbot, and analytics tools.

miele.title: Miele
miele.subtitle: Website Design
miele.descriptionSectionTwo: Miele seeks to connect its physical store and online store for customer acquisition.The brand needed an e-commerce with a consultative nature, where it connects the offline sales flow with the online capabilities.
miele.descriptionSectionThree: Develop the shopping platform in Shopify. Facilitates the process of buying premium products with great photography and a visible list of features. Automate fulfillment operations with on-demand quotes from shipping providers. Easily track returns and refunds.
miele.resultDescription: Align the requirements of the parent company with the needs of the Colombian market and customer assistance.
miele.complementDescriptionOne: HBO centrally communicates the necessary resources for commercial actions supported by gamification, a chatbot, and analytics tools.

sierracol.title: SIERRACOl ENERGY
sierracol.subtitle: Website Design
sierracol.descriptionSectionTwo: SierraCol Energy is a Colombian oil company, formerly known as Oxy de Colombia, which made a total change in its name and image. Our challenge was to create their main digital asset, their website, which aims to communicate relevant information to investors, employees and the communities where they operate. We also take care of your social networks and growth strategies
sierracol.descriptionSectionThree: We carried out a structural and functional analysis of SierraCol Energy to determine the main users and objectives to be achieved with the website. Once identified, we carry out a detailed information design process as well as a solid and scalable digital structure.
sierracol.resultDescription: As a result, we created a robust, self-managing and 100% personalized website where our UX and UI team developed its graphic environment and the organization of important data for the company.
sierracol.complementDescriptionOne: HBO centrally communicates the necessary resources for commercial actions supported by gamification, a chatbot, and analytics tools.

nextu.title: Next u
nextu.subtitle: Website Design & development
nextu.descriptionSectionTwo: Next U is an e-learning platform created by the highly successful Open English language school. They want to improve the performance of their website to increase their SEO positioning.
nextu.descriptionSectionThree: Increase the website’s performance by removing all the plugins and working with Wordpress’s core. We performed A/B Testing of the call to actions.
nextu.resultDescription: The website has higher than 90% performance according to Google Site Speed. The development was so successful the entire NextU catalog was converted to our optimized architecture.
nextu.complementDescriptionOne: We are building the digital marketing architecture to promote new advertising actions and have a better understanding of the audience through an analytics and monitoring plan.
nextu.complementDescriptionTwo: We are currently implementing local and international SEO strategies.
